observe.desc:
[
{The machine did not dispense soda or snacks, but the most eloquent of sounds.}
]

[
{He who listened to the sounds emerging from Vending Machine of Words' hatch found himself profoundly enlightened.}
]

[
{Wishing to bask in its wisdom he would return again and again, until all its knowledge had been imparted upon him.}
]

[
{However, words so divine are not to be shared; it all was for naught when the others arrived and stole his wisdom away.}
]

[
{All things come with a price. This is the one thing they came to learn in the end.}
]
